HEADWORD: Tog
<hw>Tog</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To put toggery, or
togs, on; to dress; -- usually with <xex>out</xex>, implying care,
elaborateness, or the like.</def> <mark>[Colloq. or Slang]</mark>
